moduleMetadataJson.name: Kerberos Domain User Enumeration
moduleMetadataJson.description:
This module will enumerate valid Domain Users via Kerberos from an unauthenticated perspective. It utilizes
        the different responses returned by the service for valid and invalid users.
author: Matt Byrne <attackdebris@gmail.com>

options.name: WORKSPACE
options.description: Specify the workspace for this module

options.name: RHOSTS
options.description: The target host(s), range CIDR identifier, or hosts file with syntax 'file:<path>'

options.name: Timeout
options.description: The TCP timeout to establish connection and read data

options.name: USER_FILE
options.description: Files containing usernames, one per line
